    • Method Detail

      • metrics

        TabularData metrics(boolean reset)
             throws OpenDataException
        Return the current JETM performance metrics.
        Parameters:
        reset - If true, JETM metrics are reset after the gather. If false, they are not reset and the next call will be cumulative metrics.
        Returns:
        The JETM metrics. The TabluarData includes columns: "dateOfMeasurement", "measurementPoint", "numberOfMeasurements", "average", "min", "max", "total"
        Throws:
        OpenDataException
